title: Group Therapy - Recently Divorced, Should I Start a GoFundMe?
description: Amy called the show today to let us know she wants to start a GoFundMe for getting divorced. She want's to live in a house that she can't afford and she doesn't know what else to do. What do you think? Let us know!
